! Penz config:

*font: xft:DejaVuSansMono:size=14:antialias=true:autohint=true

*Text.borderWidth: 1
*Canvas.borderWidth: 1
*Button.borderWidth: 1
*Scrollbar.borderWidth: 1
*Entry.borderWidth: 1
*Listbox.borderWidth: 1
*Menu.borderWidth: 1
*Menu.activeBorderWidth: 1
*Menu.tearOff: false
*Listbox.selectBorderWidth: 0
*Listbox.selectBackground: #0000a0
*Listbox.selectForeground: #ffffff
*Listbox.background: #ffffff

! emacs support
Emacs.font: DejaVuSansMono:size=14:antialias=true:autohint=true

